data.description:
Impeccably-maintained 2 bedroom, 2 bath corner unit, boasting views of the river and breathtaking Florida sunsets. Nestled in the sought-after Cape Shores Condominium, this community invites you to indulge in an array of phenomenal amenities. From the riverside boat dock, heated pool, games, sauna, clubhouse, and exercise room. Every aspect of comfort and enjoyment is considered.
Step into a modernized, open living space featuring quarts countertops, with built in work space and bamboo flooring throughout and newer AC (2019). The Primary bedroom offers a spacious walk in closet and sliding glass doors that open to a large, screened balcony. Extra storage space is offered in the unit and also has a separate storage closet near the onsite laundry, Just 2 doors down.
This will be a beautiful place to call home! Just a short stroll to the beach! Close proximity to SR 528, shopping districts, restaurants, parks, and grocery stores.
